        "description": "You will learn a historic craft by completing and experimenting with challenges and tacit puzzles presented in each craft\nMaster the tacit skills of historic crafts. Stay motivated to complete and experiment with old crafts challenges. \n\nHistorical objects are 1:1 models based on 3D photogrammetry and thorough studies by historians. Textures on these objects are prioritized to achieve authenticity and portray beautiful craftmanship. The experience emphasises historical accuracy so it can be used for vanicular education and historical dissemination.\n\nGetting started is easy! Brief tutorials teach you how to interact with objects and the world.\nContinuous locomotion and teleporting is supported. The experience will be supported on all Oculus VR headsets.",
